# This fixture's dependency-claim mechanism needs a real (but hand-authored,
# never `npm install`ed) node_modules/unused-lib/package.json manifest — see
# labels.yaml's case description for why. The repo-root .gitignore excludes
# every "node_modules/" directory; these two negations re-include only this
# fixture's own hand-authored one.
!node_modules/
!node_modules/**
